Use the standard library
This is how to is_simple_power of x and n:
   When x is 1, then:
      The answer is 1
   End when
   Remember that value is n
   Do this x times:
      When value is x, then:
         The answer is 1
      End when
      When value is more than x, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      Remember that value is product of value and n
   End do
   The answer is 0
Now you know

>>> is_simple_power of 1 and 4
1
>>> is_simple_power of 2 and 2
1
>>> is_simple_power of 8 and 2
1